## Summary of All Bugs Fixed

| # | Location | Bug | Fix |
|---|----------|-----|-----|
| 1 | `emitPrologue`/`emitEpilogue` | LR saved at `SP+8` (wrong slot) | Save/restore at `SP+FRAME_SIZE+4` per EABI |
| 2 | `emitExit` | CPSR not saved to frame slot before reload | Added `stw RCPSR, FRAME_CPSR` + dedicated CPSR slot |
| 3 | `condPpc` | All CR7 bit indices off by one | Fixed: Z→GT(29), C→EQ(30), N→LT(28), V→SO(31) |
| 4 | `setNZ` | Z flag extraction: wrong CR field bit rotation | Fixed: CR6[EQ] is at CR bit 5 (standard), rotate left 25 to reach bit 30 |
| 5 | `setV_add/sub` | Overflow bit placed at wrong CPSR bit | Fixed: rotate 29 places it at bit28 (V flag) |
| 6 | `setC_bit0` | Wrong rotation for carry → C flag | Fixed: rotate 29 to reach bit 29 (C flag) |
| 7 | `emitBXexit` | T-bit manipulation wrong (clear mask wrong) | Fixed: clear PPC bit26, extract Rm bit0 to bit5 |
